Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Avant============================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.87,0:00:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获得反中子干扰器的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.19,0:00:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是大功一件 阿兹拉尔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.87,0:00:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 比起动用核弹发起总攻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.43,0:00:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解决地面上日趋严重的能源危机
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.27,0:00:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是当务之急
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.07,0:00:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么还说这种话 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.92,0:00:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.20,0:00:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不下狠心赢不了这场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.91,0:00:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手又是调整人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要干就必须彻底
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.83,0:00:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说 核弹之前就用过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.16,0:00:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在何必再客气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.03,0:00:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那是你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.31,0:00:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核弹不是摆设用的陈列品
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.55,0:00:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是强力的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器就要有用武之地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.40,0:00:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花大钱打造 为得就是用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.90,0:01:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 早用早结束
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.75,0:01:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束这场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.42,0:01:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明12:00
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第六第七轨道舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.46,0:01:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开环月球轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.72,0:01:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始向PLANT防御要塞波阿斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.77,0:01:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,及PLANT本土发动攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Main============================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.35,0:03:03.17,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1188,576)}{\fad(500,0)}{\bord3\shad1\be20\an3\fs60}噩梦重现
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.35,0:03:03.17,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1188,576)}{\fad(500,0)}{\bord2\shad0\1a&HFF&\3a&H00&\an3\fs60}噩梦重现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.25,0:03:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战代号「死刑台」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展开阵型西西里3
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:06.09,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}{\bord3\shad1\be20\an2\pos(640,610)\fs60}扎夫特宇宙要塞波阿斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.55,0:03:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以下命令将由「鬼城」暗码传达
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.06,0:03:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全机 让调整人的细胞撒满宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.79,0:03:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人向波阿斯发动进攻了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.24,0:03:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玖尔队长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.83,0:03:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的自然人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.11,0:03:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况是？敌人的规模有多大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.16,0:03:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们什么时候出击？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉议长阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慌什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月球舰队进攻波阿斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是预料之外的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全军召集情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经完成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.26,0:03:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报道管制
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 已经在做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.89,0:03:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告详情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.48,0:03:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么劣质的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.53,0:04:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小看波阿斯守军
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.59,0:04:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回避
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人在左翼排开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩亚队切尼队请求支援
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮火集中覆盖左翼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.93,0:04:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈尔队前去增援
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中部战线情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾萨队正在防守
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.19,0:04:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈尔队 5号大门出击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.99,0:04:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想过波阿斯这关 有本事就来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自不量力的自然人们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.72,0:04:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:04:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想说什么 克鲁泽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突破波阿斯并非易事 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球军也应该心知肚明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不会在毫无胜算的条件下进军
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时间点上的进攻 必有缘由
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,X-131确认APU分离 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.89,0:05:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路线清空 灾祸允许出击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.85,0:05:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,X-252待命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.32,0:05:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靛青13.66B出现新机影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.28,0:05:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是机动战士 数量3
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.89,0:05:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是克鲁泽队报告的那三架
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.24,0:05:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其后方大天使级1 阿迦梅隆级4
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.66,0:05:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离500
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 增援吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:05:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多啊 上！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.15,0:06:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 眼睛都花了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊 敢朝我开枪的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.54,0:06:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么缘由 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无非就是那些机动战士部队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.12,0:06:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和几架新型机罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 以为有那些东西就攻无不克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.29,0:06:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样 自然再好不过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.37,0:06:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初阵给我消极怠工
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.31,0:06:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在看来还蛮厉害啊 他们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.22,0:06:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华盛顿号来电
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.16,0:06:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来道路已经打通
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「和平使者队」出击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.06,0:06:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底想说什么 克鲁泽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.74,0:07:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕我直言 我们仍有几个不安要素
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.17,0:07:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由 正义 拉克丝·克莱茵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平使者队 距离目标400
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.03,0:07:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以哦 你们必须陪我玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.04,0:07:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…你想说他们又搬出了核武器吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我也希望不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.46,0:07:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除保险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.02,0:07:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认信管启动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.98,0:08:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 死去吧天上的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为蓝色纯净的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.90,0:08:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月球舰队向波阿斯发起进攻？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.13,0:08:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 按他的话说就快了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.26,0:08:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者已经开始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正和大天使号通话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.63,0:08:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇呜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.56,0:08:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好炫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.65,0:09:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这热量是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核弹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.43,0:09:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不出所料 好快好快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.01,0:09:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一眨眼的功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.02,0:09:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃下几颗核弹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.81,0:09:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎夫特引以为豪的要塞也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.43,0:09:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿兹拉尔理事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.99,0:09:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就活该死于核打击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没想到会从军人嘴里听到这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样总比 命令自己部下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.91,0:09:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去参加一场毫无胜算的战斗 来得仁慈得多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 接下来轮到他们的老巢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.09,0:10:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次总算能结束了 这场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.07,0:10:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的自然人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,议长阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.91,0:10:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即部署防线
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.16,0:10:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克鲁泽 跟我去雅金·多维
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.19,0:10:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动用「创世纪」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘员立即各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.22,0:10:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.04,0:10:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘员立即各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝 要行动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.23,0:10:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月球舰队进攻波阿斯是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 事态发展得更迅速
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.64,0:10:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 正朝最糟糕的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.62,0:10:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据我们刚才收到的内部消息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.60,0:10:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波阿斯已经陷落了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地球军的核打击下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 核弹这也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒不怎么意外
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.79,0:11:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有JOSH-A的事在先
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.75,0:11:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 那个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.20,0:11:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的大门即将打开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我打开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.94,0:11:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而这个世界也将结束
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.50,0:11:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个无尽欲望的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带着钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束战争的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.62,0:11:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿兹拉尔理事！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.12,0:11:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 PLANT也会有所动作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟PLANT也有反中子干扰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.13,0:12:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰认为PLANT也会发射核弹？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的父亲 我想应该不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.48,0:12:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 我也说不准
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会有那种东西存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.49,0:12:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核武器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然机动战士和枪也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.22,0:12:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,补给工作还没完成吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.11,0:12:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 还需要一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.98,0:12:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.29,0:12:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 慢慢来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.26,0:12:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是阿拉斯加的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.31,0:12:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们对 地球军本身存有怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.24,0:12:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你确实是指挥这艘船的舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.89,0:13:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 还有人站在更高的角度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.20,0:13:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从全局上考虑指挥着这场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.59,0:13:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.67,0:13:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是留在月球基地上好些吧 现在看来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.58,0:13:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说来到前线
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.96,0:13:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一定能遇到大天使号
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我无论如何 也想见他一面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.84,0:13:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 想见面把这些事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…和其他伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.24,0:13:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 下舰桥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居住区里不会那么可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.79,0:13:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然害怕！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.14,0:13:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我始终不知道 大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明看得到 我却…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以不看就没有必要去看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.46,0:14:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面的战斗会越发白热化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.34,0:14:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像刚才那样的情形
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.69,0:14:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他明明说这样战争就会结束！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.66,0:14:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实会结束
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.19,0:14:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铲除所有异己的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.15,0:14:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实…会结束
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.12,0:14:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下 补给工作全部完成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.54,0:14:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 全舰出击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让自然人野蛮的核武大棒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:15:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续在我们的头上挥舞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.70,0:15:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情人节惨剧后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.77,0:15:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们未实施核报复的那份良苦用心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.65,0:15:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次遭到了自然人们的践踏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.27,0:15:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玖尔队 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.36,0:15:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍无可忍 已无须再忍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绿色28.13A
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离352 发现敌主力部队
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.93,0:15:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎夫特的勇士们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.10,0:15:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌舰队进入射程范围
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰 开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.49,0:15:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是展示我们力量的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.24,0:15:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.99,0:16:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁才是 这个世界新的主宰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.87,0:16:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核弹 一颗也不能让它落在PLANT
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.78,0:16:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这把光之刃 若再次刺向无辜的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将唤来无尽的悲伤与仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.61,0:16:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像比上次多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多也是菜鸟 无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无关紧要 杀就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平使者各队开始出击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.89,0:17:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们或许 为时已晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.47,0:17:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉·大和 自由出击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.94,0:17:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰·萨拉 正义出动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.35,0:17:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穆·拉·弗拉戈 强袭出击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提亚哥·埃尔斯曼 暴风出发
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.35,0:17:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「流星」启动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.26,0:17:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为和平呐喊 却手持武器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.07,0:17:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这或许 又是一次罪恶的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.70,0:17:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是请赐予我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.70,0:17:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对这无尽的仇恨锁链 斩断它的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:15.88,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)\an9}轻轻触摸 指尖的冰凉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.33,0:18:24.84,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)\an9}冰封千年 被月光照亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.49,0:18:35.26,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)\an9}碎裂的心 怀念热情的夜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:40.61,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)\an9}地平线远方 思念辉煌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.83,0:18:49.40,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)\an9}是爱的话 把它化作幻像
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:54.33,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)\an9}释放光 从天而降
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:58.84,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)\an9}竭尽所能 献上热量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.02,0:19:03.26,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)\an9}星之将亡 激发热浪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:11.91,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)\an9}将最后的梦想 烙在大地上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.04,0:18:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抹杀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.29,0:18:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙 该死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.77,0:18:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死 那是！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.39,0:18:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核弹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.32,0:18:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击落那些导弹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.58,0:18:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让它们去PLANT
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.06,0:19:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别干坏事 我要看焰火
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.06,0:19:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰？还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球军请立即停止攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.89,0:19:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这声音是 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.87,0:19:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.18,0:20:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们真的明白自己在做什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想干什么 拉克丝·克莱茵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再重复一遍 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球军请立即停止攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.26,0:20:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小丫头是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.58,0:20:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 捣乱的都是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留着那架机动战士迟早也会有麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.04,0:20:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好 让他们一起消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.73,0:20:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和PLANT一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎夫特军 宇宙要塞雅金·多维
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.08,0:20:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？拉克丝·克莱茵？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.98,0:20:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 又耍小聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.98,0:20:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管 让她去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.90,0:20:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边的准备完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.43,0:20:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创世纪进入最终发射阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰 撤离射程范围
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.51,0:20:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让部队撤下来 艾萨利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:21:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们真正的力量 让他们见识一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.20,0:21:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全军撤离射程范围
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创世纪？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.61,0:21:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创世纪 瞄准镜面就位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.42,0:21:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电压到达临界点 解除海市蜃楼系统
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.59,0:21:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创世纪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎夫特军正在撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.63,0:21:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅金·多维后方出现巨型物体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.98,0:21:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.29,0:21:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相转移装甲启动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.80,0:21:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.81,0:21:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走 正义 自由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.33,0:21:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创世纪要发射了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.95,0:21:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启动反中子干扰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.78,0:21:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核能弹仓触发位置固定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射系统一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.27,0:21:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着吧 自然人们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.12,0:21:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一击将成为调整人时代的创世之光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.92,0:22:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Next============================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.09,0:23:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿望、信念 因此拿起枪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.83,0:23:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样告诉自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.88,0:23:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 被击中时的痛楚和悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.50,0:23:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化作憎恶的漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.85,0:23:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欲吞噬一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.19,0:23:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噩梦之渊中人们挣扎着呼喊着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.53,0:23:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 机动战士高达SEED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.20,0:23:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「怒日」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.08,0:23:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斩断仇恨的锁链 高达

